# Group Project Survival Guide

How to navigate the treacherous waters of academic collaboration.

## Team Member Archetypes
- **The Ghost**: Vanishes after first meeting
- **The Control Freak**: Does everything then complains
- **The Last Minute Hero**: Saves the day (and your grade)
- **The Idea Person**: Has great ideas... for others to execute

```javascript
// How group projects actually work
const doAllTheWork = () => {
  while(deadlineApproaching) {
    panic();
    drinkCoffee();
    actuallyWork();
  }
};
```
